<P>
   GORE-VISIT (SEATTLE) _ Vice President Al Gore and his son are
vacationing on Mount Rainier as part of a private, unpublicized
family visit, an official at the White House said Wednesday. Asked
about the visit, a senior member of Gore's staff said Wednesday
night, ``The vice president is on vacation in the West with his
son,'' Albert Gore III. ``Beyond that, I cannot comment.''
</P>
<P>
   By Joel Connelly. (Story will move in the ``a'' category.)
</P>
