<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-05 12:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6647 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CHILDCARE-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      08-05 1773
