   WHITLOCK. Jason Whitlock column from Vikings training camp.
</P>
<P>
   CHIEFS. The Chiefs brought five quarterbacks to camp but
certainly won't leave with that many. Who's out and who's in? Adam
Teicher. 18-20.
</P>
<P>
   POSNANSKI. Joe Posnanski column on the Wizards' ever dwindling
support. He talked with Alexi Lalas recently about the malaise.
</P>
<P>
   ROYALS. Kevin Appier left KC so quickly, there was almost no
time to talk about his contribution to the Royals. We'll do that
here on the team's off day. Dick Kaegel. 16-18.
</P>
<P>
   MULOGO. In stores this morning, University of Missouri fans will
get their first chance to buy sweatshirts, t-shirts, key chains,
mugs and pennants bearing a new look 3-D Tiger. Mike DeArmond. 18.
</P>
<P>
   GORDON. The more he does, the more he's hated. What its like to
be the most hated person in NASCAR. Jim Pedley. 21.
</P>
