director; with Ben Stiller, Geoffrey Rush, Hank Azaria, Janeanne
Garofalo, William H. Macy, Lena Olin, Paul Reubens, Claire Forlani,
Greg Kinnear. Reviewed by Janet Maslin.
</P>
