<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Y2K WON'T BRING 'NATIONAL CATASTROPHE,' ADMINISTRATION SAYS
 &HT;    With Y2K-COLLEGES. Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial
categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
