<HEADER>
A7275 &Cx1f; ttf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FRONTPAGE-NYT &LR;      08-05 0934
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FRONTPAGE-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   (lh) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are planning for
Page 1, Friday, Aug. 6. The N.Y. Times News Service Night
Supervisor is Lynn Hoogenboom; phone: (888) 346-9867.
</P>
