<P>
   FILM-SIXTH (Undated) _ One of the great things about being a
critic is that you often see movies weeks or even months in
advance, and can actually be surprised by a film, often pleasantly.
This definitely happened to me with the Bruce Willis occult
thriller, ``The Sixth Sense.''
</P>
