   FILM-CROWN (Undated) _ Die-hard fans of the 1969 caper-romance,
``The Thomas Crown Affair,'' will probably have little use with
this 1999 remake, which lacks the movie-star presence of Steve
McQueen as its spark plug and the original's distinctive blend of
voluptuous charm and '60s cool. But non-cultists should enjoy what
is an engaging and well-acted retread.
</P>
<P>
